data.description: This 3 bedroom rambler is a charmer. Located in a well established neighborhood in a cul-de-sac! SS appliances, beautiful shaker style cabinets with quartz counter tops and full height backsplash. Tasteful flooring throughout the house, central air conditioning to cool off in those hot summer days, and a wood burning fireplace to cozy up next to in the winter. Generously sized backyard, patio, and lots of privacy. Conveniently located close to schools, shopping,  major freeways and JBLM. Stop by and fall in love today.
